those events are not always the same.

35
00:02:30,999 --> 00:02:35,150
Whether they experience an event as stressful or not is a function of their appraisals,

36
00:02:35,150 --> 00:02:37,590
their primary and secondary appraisal.

37
00:02:37,590 --> 00:02:41,540
Is this thing a threat to me or a challenge to be overcome?

38
00:02:41,540 --> 00:02:44,909
Do I have the coping resources I need?

39
00:02:44,909 --> 00:02:47,810
The appraisal is influenced by a few different things.

40
00:02:47,810 --> 00:02:50,459
