45
00:03:04,889 --> 00:03:11,090
And as a result, exams don’t tend to produce the same amount of stress as they did before.

46
00:03:11,090 --> 00:03:14,989
Controllability and predictability also produce more positive appraisals.

47
00:03:14,989 --> 00:03:18,870
We don’t find things that are controllable or predictable as stressful as things that

48
